data.description: UNDER $240,000 in Crestview!! Wonderful home!!  Well maintained!! This is a great starter or family home!!  New roof 2022!! The living space is HUGE!!  I love this home as it allows you to have a beautiful property that is well maintained at an affordable price. You also have a large fully fenced (2022) yard, a newer shed and a screened porch. When you walk in, you know this home was loved.  The owner bought this home and provided love and care.  Unfortunately, he received orders to PCS after only a year in his home and a great amount of work to this property. Finding a home that is move in ready under $250,000 is a rare find in Okaloosa County.  Do not miss this one!!
